Contols
    Player1
        Thrust:          W
        Rotate left:     A
        Rotate right:    D
        Shoot:           SPACE
    Player2
        Thrust:          UP
        Rotate left:     LEFT
        Rotate right:    RIGHT
        Shoot:           R-CTRL or R-SHIFT
    Close game: ESC

How to play
    The objective of the game is to shoot the other player
    to get the highest score.

    Shooting the other player increases score with 100 points.

    Dying reduces score wiht 100 points.

    When thrusting, fuel is depleted. Collecting a fuel can
    replenishes the players fuel.